text: The following list is of events that happened during 2013 in Kenya. ==Incumbents== *President: Mwai Kibaki (until 9 April), Uhuru Kenyatta (starting 9 April) *Deputy President: Kalonzo Musyoka (until 9 April), William Ruto (starting 9 April) *Chief Justice: Willy Mutunga *Speaker of the Senate: Ekwe Ethuro (starting 28 March) ==Events== ==Deaths== ==References==
title: 2013 in Kenya
